      "Gartner's Cool Vendors in human capital management (HCM) software for 2012 spotlights the the full employee life cycle, from workforce planning to exit.|Gartner's Cool Vendors in human capital management (HCM) software for 2012 spotlights the the full employee life cycle, from workforce planning to exit.",
