    Slug: "half-hiring-managers-say-tough-predict-long-term-success-newly-hired-talent",
    _yoast_wpseo_metadesc:
      "Visier surveyed 200 hiring managers at companies with annual revenues of $1 billion or more. Read on for their talent acquisition challenges.",
