      "Visier Announces Viser Academy, Offering Customers Deeper Insights in Workforce Analytics",
    Content:
      '<h2><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">Online education portal provides ongoing value to customers looking to maximize their workforce analytics</span></i></h2>\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>SAN JOSE, CA and VANCOUVER, BC</b><span style="font-weight: 400;"> – January 8, 2019 – </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Visier</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">, the globally recognized leader in people analytics and planning, today announced Visier Academy, an online education portal available to all Visier customers. Visier Academy provides customers with valuable tools for self-paced training, job aids, and practical solutions for getting the most out of Visier’s solution.  </span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">“Visier is committed to helping our customers use data driven insights to know their workforce better than ever. Visier Academy was created to provide our customers with the right insights and training to get the most out of Visier’s solution, while making our resources available to them whenever, and wherever, they need,” said Nigel Stoodley, Chief Customer Officer of Visier. “Visier Academy allows us to immediately provide our customers with new and updated material, in various formats for multiple uses and learning styles. We’re thrilled to offer this new resource to our current and future customers so that they can continue to realize success with Visier.”</span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Visier Academy is immediately available to all current and future customers of Visier. Through Visier Academy customers will have access to:</span>\n<ul>\n \t<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Self-paced training modules that provide overviews of the Visier People Solutions</span></li>\n \t<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Self-paced training modules on specific features within Visier People</span></li>\n \t<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Job aids to walk customers through certain workflows as they develop familiarity with the solution</span></li>\n \t<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Practical use methods, including how a variety of Visier Analysis can be put to use in your organization</span></li>\n \t<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Webinars</span></li>\n \t<li style="font-weight: 400;"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Guidance and support from customer support representatives</span></li>\n</ul>\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">“We’ve found great benefit from Visier Academy,” said Sam Thayer, Senior HR Director of Compass Group. “The comprehensive training module set has helped decrease our workload, expenses and increase our speed to deployment.”</span>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>About Visier</b>\n\nVisier’s purpose is to help people see the truth and create a better future—now.\n\nVisier was founded to focus on what matters to business people: answering the right questions, even the ones a person might not know to ask. Questions that shape business strategy, provide the impetus for taking action, and drive better business results.\n\nVisier delivers fast, clear people insight by using all the available people data—regardless of source. With best-practice expertise built-in, decision-makers can confidently take action. Thanks to our amazing customers, Visier is the market leader in Workforce Analytics with 5,000 customers in 75 countries around the world.\n\nFor more information, visit http://www.visier.com.\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<b>Contact</b>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Julie Galla</span>\n\n<a href="mailto:visier@sparkpr.com"><span style="font-weight: 400;">visier@sparkpr.com</span></a>\n\n&nbsp;',
