    id: 36881,
    Title:
      "Visier Partners with Insperity to Bring People Analytics to Mid-Market Organizations",
    Content:
      '<h2><i><span style="font-weight: 400;">Visier people analytics now has the capability to provide valuable insights for growing organizations </span></i></h2>\n&nbsp;\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">VANCOUVER, BC and SAN FRANCISCO– </span><b>April 30, 2019 </b><span style="font-weight: 400;">— </span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Visier</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">, the globally recognized leader in people analytics and planning, today announced a strategic initiative with </span><a href="https://www.insperity.com/"><span style="font-weight: 400;">Insperity</span></a> <span style="font-weight: 400;">(NYSE: NSP), a leading provider of human resources and business performance solutions for America’s best businesses. Through this partnership, people analytics will be powered by Visier on Insperity’s HR technology platform.  </span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">“Visier has long delivered the leading people analytics solution for the Global 2000 enterprise class. With this partnership with Insperity, we have extended the value of people analytics to mid-market organizations,” said John Schwarz, Founder and CEO of Visier. “Insperity is one of the country’s most comprehensive HR service providers. We are proud to power business-shaping people insights for their clients.” </span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Visier’s entrance into the mid-market sector is the result of a much anticipated strategic initiative for the company, allowing people analytics to be available to organizations of all sizes, creating opportunities for more leaders to experience the <a href="/blog/12-ways-to-go-from-administrative-hr-to-business-impact-hr/">difference that people analytics can make in the success of their company</a> and help them to gain a competitive advantage.      </span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">“Our partnership with Visier presents Insperity with a great opportunity to offer powerful HR data analytics combined with the expertise of HR professionals to deliver a new level of Software-With-A-Service unique in the marketplace,” said Paul Sarvadi, Chairman and CEO of Insperity. “Once the implementation and roll-out phase is complete later this year, it will be a game changer for our mid-market and emerging growth clients.”</span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">“Bringing our advanced capabilities to organizations at all levels has been an aspiration of Visier’s for some time now,” said Dave Weisbeck, Chief Strategy Officer of Visier. “Insperity was the perfect partner for us to be able to best position our analytics to growing organizations; not only is Insperity the leader in full-service HR solutions, but they also have the vision to see what innovative companies will need for the future of work. Through this partnership we expect to see increased value for both companies.”</span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Visier people analytics is currently in beta testing for Insperity.  The wider application will be available later in the year for Insperity’s mid-market and emerging growth clients.</span>\n\n<b>About Visier</b>\n\nVisier’s purpose is to help people see the truth and create a better future—now.\n\nVisier was founded to focus on what matters to business people: answering the right questions, even the ones a person might not know to ask. Questions that shape business strategy, provide the impetus for taking action, and drive better business results.\n\nVisier delivers fast, clear people insight by using all the available people data—regardless of source. With best-practice expertise built-in, decision-makers can confidently take action. Thanks to our amazing customers, Visier is the market leader in Workforce Analytics with 5,000 customers in 75 countries around the world.\n\nFor more information, visit http://www.visier.com.\n\n<b>About Insperity</b>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Insperity, a trusted advisor to America’s best businesses for more than 33 years, provides an array of human resources and business solutions designed to help improve business performance. Insperity</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">®</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"> Business Performance Advisors offer the most comprehensive suite of products and services available in the marketplace. Insperity delivers administrative relief, better benefits, reduced liabilities and a systematic way to improve productivity through its premier Workforce Optimization</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">®</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"> solution. Additional company offerings include Traditional Payroll and Human Capital Management, Time and Attendance, Performance Management, Organizational Planning, Recruiting Services, Employment Screening, Expense Management, Retirement Services and Insurance Services. Insperity business performance solutions support more than 100,000 businesses with over 2 million employees.  With 2018 revenues of $3.8 billion, Insperity operates in 74 offices throughout the United States. For more information, visit</span> <a href="https://www.insperity.com"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://www.insperity.com</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400;">. </span>\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;"># # # </span>\n\n&nbsp;\n\n<span style="font-weight: 400;">Contact:</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">\n</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">Julie Galla</span><span style="font-weight: 400;">\n</span><a href="mailto:visier@sparkpr.com"><span style="font-weight: 400;">visier@sparkpr.com</span></a>',
    Excerpt: "",
    Date: "2019-04-30",
    Permalink:
      "https://www.visier.com/press-release/visier-partners-with-insperity-to-bring-people-analytics-to-mid-market-organizations/",
    Slug: "visier-partners-with-insperity-to-bring-people-analytics-to-mid-market-organizations",
    _yoast_wpseo_metadesc:
      "Visier announced a strategic initiative with Insperity, a leading provider of HR and business performance solutions for America’s best businesses.",
