    Slug: "people-analytics-leader-visier-announces-appointment-nick-lisi-chief-sales-officer",
    _yoast_wpseo_metadesc:
      "Visier, the recognized leader in people analytics and planning, today announced the appointment of Nick Lisi as the company’s Chief Sales Officer.",
